OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1779012401
OL,3,CSoldier dies after falling from horse
OL,4,Cat Royal Windsor Show
OL,6,FA service person has died after
OL,7,Ffalling from their horse at the Royal
OL,8,FWindsor Horse Show on Friday evening
OL,9,Ffollowing a display.
OL,11,FThe soldier, who was a member of the
OL,12,FKing's Troop, Royal Horse Artillery
OL,13,Ffell having exited the arena following
OL,14,Ftheir display.
OL,16,FDespite being given immediate medical
OL,17,Ftreatment they died at the scene from
OL,18,Ftheir serious injuries.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
