PN,41402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1779012401
OL,3,CSoldier dies after falling from horse
OL,4,Cat Royal Windsor Show
OL,6,FTheir next of kind have been informed
OL,7,Fand are being supported by specialist
OL,8,Fofficers.
OL,10,FThames Valley Police say the death was
OL,11,Fsuspicious but unexplained as they
OL,12,Finvestigate what happened.
OL,14,FThe force is asking witnesses with
OL,15,Fvideo or photographs of the event to
OL,16,Fget in touch.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
