PN,41403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1779012401
OL,3,CSoldier dies after falling from horse
OL,4,Cat Royal Windsor Show
OL,6,FChief Superintendent Michael
OL,7,FLoebenberg said: "We are appealing for
OL,8,Fanyone with information or material
OL,9,Frelating to the sad death of a
OL,10,Fmilitary rider at Royal Windsor Horse
OL,11,FShow yesterday to please get in touch.
OL,13,F"Our thoughts are with the soldier's
OL,14,Ffamily and the wider community in the
OL,15,Fmilitary and at the Royal Windsor
OL,16,FHorse Show at this extremely difficult
OL,17,Ftime.
OL,26,@oD@ROUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
