PN,41404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1779012401
OL,3,CSoldier dies after falling from horse
OL,4,Cat Royal Windsor Show
OL,6,F"At this stage, we have not found any
OL,7,Fsuspicious circumstances. We are
OL,8,Fworking with the Ministry of Defence,
OL,9,Fthe Defence Accident Investigation
OL,10,FBranch and Royal Windsor Horse Show
OL,11,Forganisers HPower to gather as much
OL,12,Finformation as possible to understand
OL,13,Fhow this happened."
OL,15,FThe prestigious four-day equestrian
OL,16,Fbegan on Thursday n the private
OL,17,Fgrounds of Windsor Castle. Despite the
OL,18,Ftragedy, organisers said the event
OL,19,Fwill largely continue.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@SO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
