PN,41405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1779012401
OL,3,CSoldier dies after falling from horse
OL,4,Cat Royal Windsor Show
OL,6,FJo Peck, HPower Event Director, said:
OL,7,F"Our thoughts and sympathies are with
OL,8,Fthe family of the soldier who sadly
OL,9,Fdied yesterday. The Royal Windsor
OL,10,FHorse Show will continue today as per
OL,11,Fthe published timetable, with the
OL,12,Fomission of The King's Troop, Royal
OL,13,FHorse Artillery display."
OL,15,FAnyone with information should call
OL,16,F101, make a report on the police's
OL,17,Fwebsite, speak to a police officer at
OL,18,Fthe horse show or visit a police
OL,19,Fstation, quoting reference number 521
OL,20,Fof today's date.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@YO]
